{
  "stem": "27507.10",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what happened was that Koper started hiding Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first person that he hid, or one of the very first, was my Aunt Hania, who came to him more or less straight of the ghetto, and who is still alive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after her, somebody else came into this flat, and somebody else, and somebody else, and my father, after he escaped from that Lorry was somehow brought there as well.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I was brought there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody was thrown out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, suddenly, there were 11 Jews hiding in this little flat, apart from the house owners, who were a couple, Koper and his wife Marta, Marta.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lodger-- there was a lodger as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it didn't look like in the middle of the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looked like an outskirts, like some kind of a pretty vague area on the outskirts of the city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, it was in this pretty much in the center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this house, this wooden house where Koper lived, Koper got it because it was this flat-- because he worked for the army, or for the border guard director, something like that, before the war.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that belonged-- all the flats, belonged, I think, to the army, or to army formations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they lived there almost as if it was in the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- the front door was leading to the garden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a garden in front, a large garden, where Marta, the wife of Koper, was having a beautiful garden with vegetables, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because of the garden, you couldn't exactly see who was coming in front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even the front window was not very-- was covered by vegetation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And side windows were open to the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
